    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as being in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously garaged and pampered, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple leather upholstery that shows no signs of wear, perfectly preserved trim, and all original accessories in working order. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with full documentation included. Every gear shift is seamless, and the engine retains its factory-fresh responsiveness. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. A viewing is essential to appreciate the level of care this car has received.",
      "price": 46500.0,
