    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It's in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, clean feel inside. I'm really going to miss it, but I'm excited for it to go to someone who will love it just as much as I have. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
