      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, breathing through six individual throttle bodies and delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is tightened by a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these cars are known for. Finished in a deep luster with zero rock chips, the interior boasts supple Nappa leather and an unblemished dashboard. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
